                     <interp inst="t17780603-37-person292" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            , a pawnbroker, produced the watch, which he deposed he received of Draper.]</p>
               <p>[The prisoners were not put on their defence.]</p>
               <p>BOTH <rs id="t17780603-37-verdict179" type="verdictDescription">
